title: Amika Obliphica Nourishing Mask, 16.9 Fl Oz
description:
profound hydration and total indulgence For ultimate repair and deep conditioning, the Obliphica Nourishing Hair Mask directly penetrates the surface of the hair for ultimate replenishment. Used weekly, this fortifying hydrator infuses locks with extra moisture, while sealing spilt ends - resulting in total hair recovery and restoration.

The complete Obliphica Hair Care collection gets its power by harnessing the unique properties of the sea buckthorn berry, also known as obliphica. Obliphica has an unusually high content of the anti-oxidant vitamin C (15 times greater than an orange), vitamin E, omegas 3, 6, and 9 and the rare omega 7 (usually only found in fish oil). These potent vitamins and nutrients combined with the powerful properties of the argan nut oil come together to form a line that replenishes, moisturizes, and brings out the hair's natural balance.
